                        <div class="card border-0 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s" style="visibility: visible; animation-delay: 0.2s; animation-name: fadeInUp;">
                            <div class="card-header bg-light shadow" id="headingOne">
                                <h6 class="mb-0 collapsed h5" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">What is Debt/Loan Settlement?<span class="lni-chevron-up"></span></h6>
                            </div>
                            <div class="collapse" id="collapseOne" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="card-body bg-light">
                                    <p>
                                        Debt/Loan Settlement means settling debt for less than what is owed by negotiating with the lenders. CONFIRM’s Debt/Loan Settlement program is right choice for people who are so overwhelmed with debt that they cannot figure out a solution on their own.

                                        CONFRIM will help you plan your settlement using a disciplined and strategic approach. The Journey to Debt/Loan settlement is difficult, but there is financial freedom and lots of happiness at the end of this journey.
                                    </p>

                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card border-0 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.3s" style="visibility: visible; animation-delay: 0.3s; animation-name: fadeInUp;">
                            <div class="card-header shadow  bg-light" id="headingTwo">
                                <h6 class="mb-0 collapsed h5" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseTwo">What will the service cost me?<span class="lni-chevron-up"></span></h6>
                            </div>
                            <div class="collapse" id="collapseTwo" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="card-body  bg-light">
                                    <p>
                                        CONFIRM charges a very nominal subscription fee for the duration of your debt settlement program. We understand that dealing with debt is stressful, the subscription fee entitles you for the following benefits – Dedicated Expert Debt Advisory who helps you to deal with harassment, pre-litigation support, lender communication & negotiation, repayment plan, monthly budgeting, and counselling

                                        An average client usually pays a fee of 2-5% of the total debt enrolled in the program. And if we can’t settle your accounts, we refund your money. It’s that simple.
                                    </p>

                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card border-0 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.3s" style="visibility: visible; animation-delay: 0.3s; animation-name: fadeInUp;">
                            <div class="card-header shadow  bg-light" id="heading">
                                <h6 class="mb-0 collapsed h5" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse3" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse3">Will the program impact my credit score?<span class="lni-chevron-up"></span></h6>
                            </div>
                            <div class="collapse" id="collapse3" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="card-body  bg-light">
                                    <p>
                                        Depending on your personal situation and whether you have already missed payments to your lenders, debt settlement programs may have either a negative or positive impact on your credit score. Our goal is to help you get out of debt as fast as possible by negotiating with your lenders to get them to accept significantly less than what they owe.

                                        If you are already behind on your payments, chances are that your credit score has already taken a hit and the negative effects of our program on your score may not be as substantial. Infact, your credit scores generally tend to improve quickly once a debt settlement program has been completed.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card border-0 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.4s" style="visibility: visible; animation-delay: 0.4s; animation-name: fadeInUp;">
