                                <h6 class="mb-0 collapsed h5" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#collapse4" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseThree">Can I negotiate with the lenders on my own? <span class="lni-chevron-up"></span></h6>
                            </div>
                            <div class="collapse" id="collapse4" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-parent="#faqAccordion">
                                <div class="card-body  bg-light">
                                    <p>Although a Do-It-Yourself (DIY) approach might sound good, it is not the most efficient one. Debt Settlement is complex and time-consuming activity. At CONFIRM, we take care of every detail of debt negotiations – helping you overcome the most significant roadblocks that are standing in the way of your financial independence. We have the relevant experience dealing with 100s of banks & NBFCs and know the tricks of negotiation. Our deep knowledge of the regulations around lending and understanding of the rights of the borrowers, helps to negotiate best settlement and outcome for you.</p>

                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card border-0 wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.4s" style="visibility: visible; animation-delay: 0.4s; animation-name: fadeInUp;">
